      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays sparkling. It drives like a total dream and you won't find a single blemish on it. I'd love for it to go to a new home where it'll be just as loved. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person!",
      "price": 43500.0,
